Tom Bower's new book is said to be focused on Meghan, and could include her ex-husband Trevor Engelson. Royal expert Neil Sean believes Mr Engelson could have "an axe to grind" as we "only know her version of events". Speaking on his YouTube channel he said: "This particular individual would truly have a remarkable story because, after all, he would have first-hand experience of what it was like, yes what it was like, to be married the first time around to the actress from Suits." FOLLOW BELOW FOR UPDATES... 